Commentary Text: Axar to Rahul, out Caught by Daniel Sams! That's an absolute brainfade from Rahul. A Chennai-199 moment. He's slowed this down a little without altering the flat trajectory, preventing Rahul from getting under that successfully as he charges down the track to try and loft it over mid-on - manages to flat-bat it straight to Sams at mid-on, and looks absolutely livid with himself. No point, really. Quite a key moment in this run-chase. Rahul c Daniel Sams b Axar 15(11) [4s-1 6s-1]
